T1  - Structural Change and Performance: Quantum Versus Piecemeal-Incremental Approaches
AU  - Miller, Danny
AU  - Friesen, Peter H.
Y1  - 1982/12/01
PY  - 1982
DA  - 1982/12/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/256104
