T1  - A Comparison of the Practical Utility of Traditional, Statistical, and Hybrid Job Evaluation Approaches1
AU  - Gomez-Mejia, Luis R.
AU  - Page, Ronald C.
AU  - Tornow, Walter R.
Y1  - 1982/12/01
PY  - 1982
DA  - 1982/12/01
